1
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,480
She was clearly dead.

2
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:27,640
She was clearly dead.

3
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:29,920
She died.

4
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:30,450
Let's go.

5
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:38,410
She died.

6
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:40,160
She died.

7
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,000
After the play,

8
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:51,440
I went to Xiaotangchun's house.

9
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,759
I saw Xiaotangchun acting crazy,

10
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:55,020
standing on the stage.

11
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:57,130
I took the dagger I had prepared

12
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,160
and went to her house.

13
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:01,480
I stabbed her with the knife I prepared.

14
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:02,800
I killed her.

15
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:06,280
Then Meng San suddenly came out of the room.

16
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,720
So I killed him too.

17
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,000
Finally,

18
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,480
I aimed the red-tasseled spear at Xiaotangchun's wound

19
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:13,410
and stabbed her,

20
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:17,380
posing her in the 'Sleeping Fish' position.

21
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,760
What did you use to kill Meng San?

22
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:21,250
A dagger.

23
00:02:22,400 --> 00:02:24,130
When you killed Xiaotangchun,

24
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:25,640
what weapon did you use?

25
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:26,600
A dagger.

26
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,800
Single-edged or double-edged?

27
00:02:28,800 --> 00:02:29,660
Double-edged.

28
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,490
Are you sure it was a dagger,

29
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:33,000
and not a military knife?

30
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,120
I forgot.

31
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,329
I forgot.

32
00:02:37,160 --> 00:02:38,620
So you don't actually know

33
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:40,780
what Jin Guizhi used to kill Meng San.

34
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:42,880
Or you simply don't know

35
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:45,140
what Yu Jiupu used to kill Xiaotangchun.

36
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,840
Jin Guizhi wasn't there.

37
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,600
I did it all myself.

38
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:49,640
Then why are you wearing

39
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:51,000
Yun Feiyan's clothes?

40
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:52,960
Yesterday on stage,

41
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:56,360
you publicly admitted you had been defiled on purpose.

42
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,680
Then at night,

43
00:02:57,800 --> 00:03:00,680
you deliberately led us to that one-eyed man's house.

44
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,320
You did it to let us know

45
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,960
about the evil things Meng San and Xiao Tangchun

46
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,240
did to you back then.

47
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:07,120
Jin Guizhi must have thought

48
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:09,400
you had already taken the 12 o'clock train that day

49
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,360
to Beiping.

50
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,840
But you didn't want to just walk away.

51
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,000
And you also knew

52
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:15,840
that we would definitely find out

53
00:03:15,840 --> 00:03:17,400
the murderer of Yun Feiyan

54
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,560
was Xiao Tangchun.

55
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:19,720
In this way,

56
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:21,480
you and Yun Feiyan

57
00:03:21,480 --> 00:03:23,360
would have a strong motive

58
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,880
to conspire to kill Meng San and Xiao Tangchun.

59
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:28,120
You created the illusion that Jin Fengming was still alive

60
00:03:28,120 --> 00:03:30,760
because you were afraid we would suspect him immediately.

61
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:31,640
You did this

62
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,800
for only one reason:

63
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,520
to protect Yu Jiupu.

64
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,540
You want to take the blame for her.

65
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,880
But do you realize

66
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:44,160
that doing this is actually hurting her?

67
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,480
Given her motive,

68
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:47,120
along with other witnesses and evidence,

69
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:49,650
she would likely receive a lighter sentence.

70
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:51,730
But if you don't tell the truth,

71
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,200
not only will she be sentenced,

72
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:55,730
but her punishment could be even more severe.

73
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,900
The show starts in 30 minutes.

74
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,520
Once she's on stage,

75
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,450
she won't have a chance.

76
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:15,320
If I'm not mistaken,

77
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:18,000
he should have turned himself in by now.

78
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,240
That's why

79
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,680
he hasn't left.

80
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:23,520
Because he wants to take the blame

81
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:25,160
for those two lives alone.

82
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,760
You must tell us the truth now,

83
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:29,600
so we can help you.

84
00:04:30,400 --> 00:04:31,880
The law is merciless,

85
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:34,740
but beneath the robes are living people.

86
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:36,740
You think you're helping him,

87
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:39,370
but you're actually pushing him to his death.

88
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:42,640
Alright.

89
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,220
I'll tell you everything.

90
00:04:50,480 --> 00:04:51,080
I'll talk.

91
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:54,780
I went to Xiaotangchun's house that day.

92
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,360
Senior Brother.

93
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:28,650
Senior Brother,

94
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,480
come here.

95
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,760
The audience is getting impatient.

96
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:34,250
Senior Brother,

97
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:36,600
I've thought it through.

98
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,020
Since you don't want to leave,

99
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,080
we'll sing together.

100
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:43,300
The stage will be ours from now on.

101
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:52,159
That Jin Fengming wants to steal your role.

102
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,760
I found it.

103
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,140
I snatched it back for you.

104
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:57,330
Senior Brother.

105
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,370
Why did you force me?

106
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,160
Why force me?

107
00:06:38,280 --> 00:06:39,320
Senior Brother.

108
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:45,520
Senior Brother.

109
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:16,280
She killed Fengming.

110
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,560
She's a murderer.

111
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,040
She's the real murderer.

112
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,160
I... I'm not.

113
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:21,040
I'm not.

114
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:21,760
I'm here.

115
00:07:21,760 --> 00:07:22,120
Don't be afraid.

116
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:22,580
I'm not.

117
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:24,960
I'm not.

118
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:29,880
No.

119
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,700
You can't go out like this.

120
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:33,520
Listen.

121
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:34,840
Bolt the door.

122
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:36,040
Wait until I get back.

123
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,520
I came back,

124
00:07:58,520 --> 00:08:00,880
found a set of clothes left by Boss Yun,

125
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:03,200
brought along a used lipstick,

126
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:05,640
and returned to Xiaotangchun's house.

127
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,440
After you leave,

128
00:08:09,440 --> 00:08:11,040
find a place to throw it away.

129
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,480
Remember,

130
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:17,800
you were never here.

131
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:20,410
You must catch the train at 12:00 noon,

132
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,600
then write a letter to Fengming,

133
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,960
telling him to meet you in Beiping in three days.

134
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:25,920
From then on,

135
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:27,440
Fengming will be in Beiping,

136
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:28,500
together with you.

137
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:29,920
Go.

138
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:31,960
Go.

139
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,490
Don't come back.

140
00:09:46,680 --> 00:09:48,640
I intended to stage it as a suicide,

141
00:09:50,640 --> 00:09:52,520
just like she did to Boss Yun.

142
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:53,600
But you discovered

143
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:55,480
that you couldn't find the dagger.

144
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:56,610
Because that dagger

145
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:59,290
was in the clothes Yu Jiupu changed out of.

146
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:29,480
Pauper.

147
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,680
Pest.

148
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,720
No wonder.

149
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:15,640
So it's you.

150
00:12:20,280 --> 00:12:21,880
Come out.

151
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:23,920
We can talk.

152
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:30,680
Everything is negotiable.

153
00:12:41,640 --> 00:12:43,480
I plunged the red-tasseled spear

154
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,010
into Xiaotangchun's chest

155
00:12:45,880 --> 00:12:47,410
to hide the previous wound,

156
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:50,610
and arranged the body in the Woyu pose.

157
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:07,920
Then I continued singing.

158
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:10,810
As long as the neighbors could hear me,

159
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:12,180
once it hit twelve,

160
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,920
and Jiupu boarded the train,

161
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:16,180
everything would be fine.

162
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:20,040
You want us to believe...

163
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:22,920
Xiaotangchun and Meng San got into an argument.

164
00:13:22,920 --> 00:13:26,180
Xiaotangchun killed Meng San and then committed suicide.

165
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:28,960
But bodies don't lie.

166
00:13:29,520 --> 00:13:30,280
Every crime

167
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:31,840
leaves a trace.

168
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:34,080
That's right.

169
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:36,040
I just remembered something.

170
00:13:36,040 --> 00:13:39,040
Back in the opera troupe, a child fell into a water vat.

171
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:41,040
When the patrolmen arrived,

172
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:41,840
they just looked at his skin

173
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:43,640
and knew how long he'd been dead.

174
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:46,360
I know.

175
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:50,130
I couldn't hide it anymore.

176
00:13:50,640 --> 00:13:52,360
So you thought of Boss Yun.

177
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:55,840
Someone who could take the fall for Yu Jiupu.

178
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:58,400
You said Yu Jiupu is stubborn

179
00:13:58,800 --> 00:13:59,760
and inflexible.

180
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:04,240
But you'd feel safe

181
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,680
entrusting Fengming to him.

182
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:09,960
Because he is stubbornly devoted

183
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:11,200
to Fengming, too.

184
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:15,360
His whole heart

185
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:17,020
is filled with her.

186
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,040
Now that child,

187
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:19,680
for Fengming's sake,

188
00:14:19,680 --> 00:14:21,400
has caused a huge disaster.

189
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:28,800
I can't cover it up on my own anymore.

190
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:31,840
So,

191
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:34,480
you took Boss Yun's body

192
00:14:34,680 --> 00:14:36,880
and intentionally left scratch marks.

193
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:38,520
You wanted us to think

194
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:40,160
Yun Feiyan was still alive.

195
00:14:41,160 --> 00:14:42,560
So that you and Yun Feiyan

196
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:44,720
could take the blame for him.

197
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:49,160
Why is it that the more I care about someone,

198
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:50,690
the less I can protect them?

199
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:53,250
If you hadn't poisoned Xiaotangchun,

200
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:56,000
she wouldn't have lost her mind.

201
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:59,280
Maybe Jin Fengming wouldn't have died.

202
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:02,800
I shouldn't have let Fengming sing that opera.

203
00:15:05,400 --> 00:15:07,080
If Boss Yun finds out,

204
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:10,080
he will surely blame me.

205
00:15:34,560 --> 00:15:36,690
Aren't you afraid I'll just walk away?

206
00:15:38,040 --> 00:15:39,640
This is the International Settlement.

207
00:15:39,640 --> 00:15:40,840
I have no jurisdiction here.

208
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:41,640
You can leave.

209
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:44,320
I have no power to detain you.

210
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,120
And,

211
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:47,360
this place is only

212
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:49,440
a five-minute drive from the train station.

213
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:50,700
You can have a new life.

214
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:54,530
I changed the meeting place to here

215
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:58,200
because I wanted to give you back the dignity you deserve.

216
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,040
Of course,

217
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:02,560
you can also choose to face all this.

218
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:11,400
Thank you.
